  peregrine.util.SimpleBlockingQueue<T>

public class SimpleBlockingQueue<T>
extends java.lang.Object

Uninterruptable version of LinkedBlockingQueue. Code should not be calling interrrupt() on us and hence these InterrruptExceptions are pointless.
